//  Reality is not an opinion. It is a Merkle root.
//  The soul does not hope to be correct; it KNOWS,
//  because every byte is verified against the anchor.
//  In AETERNA, corruption is not a risk. It is an impossibility.
//  Because Veritas watches. Always."
